paragraph 1: 6.3 Changes in group structure
paragraph 2: Discontinued operations
paragraph 3: On 21 December 2018, the Group executed a share sale agreement to sell Infochoice Pty Ltd, a wholly owned subsidiary.
paragraph 4: At 30 June 2019, Infochoice Pty Ltd was classified as a discontinued operation. The business of Infochoice Pty Ltd represented the Group’s financial services and products comparison operating segment. With Infochoice Pty Ltd being classified as a discontinued operation, its operating results are no longer presented in the segment note. The sale of Infochoice Pty Ltd was completed on 18 February 2019. The results of Infochoice Pty Ltd for the period are presented below:
